<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="9cbee7fb-0432-4ef2-a38e-73c30aff5685" >

    <h3>Good examples&nbsp;</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Learn more <a href="/content/ryerson/about/">about Ryerson University.</a></li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/it-conference/">Register for the Ryerson IT Conference</a></li> 
 <li>There are three species of bears in North America: <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_black_bear">American black bears,<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a> <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brown_bear">brown bears,<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a> and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Polar_bear">polar bears.<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, external link</span></a></li> 
 <li>Visit <a href="/content/ryerson/admissions/">Admissions</a></li> 
</ul>
    





</div>
