<div class="res-text richtextContent background-opaque" id="91620dcc-a4aa-447d-b17a-24e0e72ff88a" >

    <h3>Bad examples&nbsp;</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/about/">Learn more</a> about Ryerson University.</li> 
 <li><a href="/content/ryerson/it-conference/">Register</a> for the Ryerson IT Conference</li> 
