    <h2><a name="forms" id="forms"></a>Forms and labels</h2> 
<p>All form fields should have accurate labels that programmatically correspond with each other using the input’s <strong>id </strong>attribute and label’s <strong>for</strong> attribute. The keyboard focus order should also match the visual order of the form.</p>
    





</div>
